            Code Block
            ========

            ## Backticks

            ````javascript
            ```javascript
            class Example {
                constructor() {
                    this.prop = [];
                }

                doit(arg) {
                    console.log(arg);
                }
            }
            ```
            ````
            Produces...

            ```javascript
            class Example {
                constructor() {
                    this.prop = [];
                }

                doit(arg) {
                    console.log(arg);
                }
            }
            ```

            ## Or just indent...

            ```
                class Example
                    constructor: ->
                        @prop = []

                    doit: (arg) =>
                        console.log arg
